        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1900217048" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13428890827579292109">ADORED this one even more then The Bride! Perfect hero and heroine! I loved how enchanted by her he was from the very beginning! And her wild spirit and sassiness were fantastic! They really brought to surface his OTT alpha protectiveness -even though she could defend herself better than anyone - and possessiveness, as well as love and caring! Completely swoon worthy! <br/><b>Lyon and his Lioness really were PERFECT</b></span>

          </span>
