<div id="review_1561546065" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1561546065" />
    <a title="Mindy Lou&#39;s Book Review" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/44132489-mindy-lou-s-book-review"><img alt="Mindy Lou&#39;s Book Review" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1465424458p2/44132489.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1561546065?book_show_action=true">Feb 26, 2016</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Mindy Lou&#39;s Book Review" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Mindy Lou&#39;s Book Review" href="/user/show/44132489-mindy-lou-s-book-review">Mindy Lou&#39;s Book Review</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/44132489-mindy-lou-s-book-review?shelf=hist-romance">hist-romance</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/44132489-mindy-lou-s-book-review?shelf=2019">2019</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1561546065" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12103944404848801094">This is one of my very, favorites from this author. I love the way Lyon reacts to Christina and how he pursues her. Especially when he is still bitter about what happened with his first wife. He&apos;s never opened himself up until Christina and I like how he realizes without much fight that she is different.<br/><br/>Christina is also why this book is a favorite. I love the way she was raised and how that impacted her life. I&apos;ve always enjoyed the strong, independent heroines and it&apos;s icing on the cake when t</span>
  <span id="freeText12103944404848801094" style="display:none">This is one of my very, favorites from this author. I love the way Lyon reacts to Christina and how he pursues her. Especially when he is still bitter about what happened with his first wife. He's never opened himself up until Christina and I like how he realizes without much fight that she is different.<br /><br />Christina is also why this book is a favorite. I love the way she was raised and how that impacted her life. I've always enjoyed the strong, independent heroines and it's icing on the cake when they have a sweet personality layered with that strength.<br /><br />I also enjoyed the romance we get to see develop with a couple of the side characters. Great book!</span>
  <a data-text-id="12103944404848801094" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


