      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/3245791-the-lion-s-lady">Quotes from The Lion&#39;s Lady</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
