            <span class="readable">&ldquo;Lyon knew she wasn't aware she was being watched, either. She wouldn't have eaten the leaf otherwise, or reached for another. <br /><br />“Sir, which one is Princess Christina?” Andrew asked Lyon, just as Rhone started in choking on his laughter. Rhone has obviously been watching Christina, too. <br /><br />“Sir?”<br /><br />“The blond-headed one,” Lyon muttered, shaking his head. He watched in growing disbelief as Christina daintily popped another leaf into her mouth. <br /><br />“Which blond-headed one?” Andrew persisted.<br /><br />“The one eating the shrubs.&rdquo;</span>
            <nobr>
              &mdash;
